{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Neo Light</strong> is a vibrant, hand-drawn 2D platformer that blends the fast-paced thrill of speedrunning with the challenge of precision gameplay. Dive into colorful stages that demand skill and strategy, all while enjoying a satirical twist on the platformer genre. Inspired by classic favorites, but with a sharp sense of humor, you'll use unique \u201clights\u201d to avoid obstacles and clear levels. Whether you\u2019re chasing that perfect run or conquering the toughest challenges, Neo Light is here to test your reflexes, dexterity and precision with a bit of satirical fun along the way! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983530/extras/Gif15.gif?t=1734085858\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness 9 unique powers to outsmart enemies and overcome challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle 6 epic bosses, each with their own quirky twist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump, crouch, and slide to recharge your powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Conquer 30 diverse levels, each split into 3 ever-changing sections</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 6 vibrant stages, each packed with its own distinct style and surprises</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983530/extras/Gif5.gif?t=1734085858\" /><br><br><br>Trailer song: Zachz Winner - blu [NCS Release]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734085858","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983530/page.bg.jpg?t=1734085858","capsule_imag